title: GoPro: Aaron Chase Teaches Mountain Biking to Toddlers
description:
Legendary mountain biker Aaron Chase teaches his young son and nephew the importance of keeping your hands on the handlebars when riding trails.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera

Music
Ravenna Woods "We Want It All"
